OL,11,Fsince they took over the territory
OL,12,Ffrom Britain, ITV News' Asia
OL,13,FCorrespondent Debi Edwards reports
OL,15,FThe heightened security around West
OL,16,FKowloon court remained in place on the
OL,17,Ffinal day of the trial of Hong Kong's
OL,18,Fmost high-profile prisoner.
