OL,7,FThe case against Jimmy Lai was drawn
OL,8,Fout over more than eighteen months,
OL,9,Fone hundred and sixty days in court,
OL,10,Ftwice as long as expected.
OL,12,FThe Hong Kong media tycoon and
OL,13,Fprominent pro-democracy supporter was
OL,14,Farrested in 2020, just weeks after
OL,15,FBeijing imposed the National Security
OL,16,FLaw (NSL).
OL,18,FHe had long been an opponent of the
OL,19,FChinese Communist Party and was among
OL,20,Fthe first group of people to be
OL,21,Fdetained under the new law.
