OL,7,FThe Asia Director for HRW, Elaine
OL,8,FPearson, said: "You had many media
OL,9,Foutlets, independent media outlets, in
OL,10,FHong Kong, most of those have been
OL,11,Fshuttered, including Apple Daily,
OL,12,Fwhich was founded by Jimmy Lai.
OL,13,FCensorship is very prevalent, and
OL,14,Fthere's so much fear amongst Hong Kong
OL,15,Fpeople that self-censorship,
OL,16,Funfortunately, has become the norm."
OL,18,FThe UK Government has called on the
OL,19,FHong Kong authorities to release Jimmy
OL,20,FLai, who is a British citizen. There
OL,21,Fis growing concern for his health.
