OL,7,FThe 77-year-old has spent the last
OL,8,Ffive years in solitary confinement; he
OL,9,Fhas diabetes and has developed heart
OL,10,Fproblems.
OL,12,FThe Chinese government has described
OL,13,FJimmy Lai as a representative of anti-
OL,14,FChina forces and of destabilising Hong
OL,15,FKong.
OL,17,FThe Hong Kong authorities have accused
OL,18,Fforeign governments of judicial
OL,19,Finterference and glorifying criminal
OL,20,Fbehaviour.
