OL,7,FThey also claim Mr Lai requested to be
OL,8,Fkept apart from other prisoners,
OL,9,Fsomething his son rejects.
OL,11,FJimmy Lai's son, Sebastian, warned
OL,12,Fthat his father's eventual death in
OL,13,Fprison if given a life sentence would
OL,14,Fhave "consequences".
OL,16,F"He didn't ask for it. It wouldn't be
OL,17,Flogical to do so, but I think that
OL,18,Fthat's also aimed to distract from the
OL,19,Fgreater issue, which is that he
OL,20,Fshouldn't be in jail in the first
OL,21,Fplace," Jimmy's son said.
