OL,7,FTrials under the national security law
OL,8,Fare being held without a jury and by a
OL,9,Fpanel of judges approved by the
OL,10,Fgovernment, leading to questions about
OL,11,Fthe fairness of the legal process.
OL,13,FThere has been an almost 100%
OL,14,Fconviction rate so far. A conviction
OL,15,Ffor Jimmy Lai means he would likely
OL,16,Fdie in prison.
OL,18,FPearson believes the verdict is a
OL,19,Fforegone conclusion.
